{"url": "https://metro.co.uk/2017/04/10/chris-pratt-singing-to-his-cream-scone-cheat-meal-is-everyone-with-diet-struggles-6565091/", "text": "Chris Pratt serenading cream scones is everyone on a diet (Picture: Instagram)\n\nChris Pratt has encompassed the beautiful joys of the dieting \u2018cheat meal\u2019 by serenading a scone before an ever-so-sweet nosh.\n\nThe 37-year-old actor is frequently watching his weight for Hollywood roles like Guardians Of The Galaxy, and has resorted to regularly documenting his dieting treats via series #WhatsMySnack on Instagram.\n\nThis episode however is the Oscar moment. He\u2019s singing those treats straight to the Academy.\n\nTo view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that supports HTML5 video Up Next Previous Page Next Page\n\nIn the clip, Pratt can be seen on the River Thames (according to the brilliant caption) wolfing down the sweet delight while crooning The Beatles track, Oh! Darling.\n\nHe also gives a shout-out to wife Anna Faris for the sumptuous cinematography. Academy noms all-round.\n\nThis isn\u2019t the only time he\u2019s captured his guilty alone-time however, having previously dedicated a rap to a carrot cake muffin.\n\nIncredible.\n\nAnd if you\u2019re a fan of healthy snacks, you can watch this episode based around an egg and cucumber wrap before leaving the room to never return.\n\nPratt is currently out promoting Guardians Of The Galaxy Vol. 2, where he stars alongside Zoe Saldana, Dave Bautista, Michael Rooker and Karen Gillan.\n\nGuardians Of The Galaxy Vol. 2 releases in UK cinemas on April 28.\n\nArrow MORE: Chris Pratt owns his body shamers in typical Chris Pratt style", "images": ["https://metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/SEC_272018625-7d16.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&w=646&h=363&crop=1", "https://metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/SEC_275022295-294b.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&w=320&h=180&crop=1", "https://metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/chris-pra